# ADMIN — PLUGINS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List plugins
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/plugins
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List plugins — type filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/plugins?type=worker
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Create plugin
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/plugins
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "demo-plugin",
  "name": "Demo Plugin",
  "description": "REST Client smoke test",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "type": "integration",
  "status": "inactive",
  "category": "demo"
}

###

### Get plugin
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/plugins/{{pluginId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update plugin
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/plugins/{{pluginId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "active"
}

###

### Bulk plugin actions
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/plugins/bulk/actions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": ["00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001"],
  "action": "setStatus",
  "status": "active"
}

###

### Delete plugin
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/plugins/{{pluginId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ADMIN — CMS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List media
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/media
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Upload media
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/media
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=B

--B
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="photo.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./samples/photo.jpg
--B
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="alt"

Dev Hube logo
--B--

###

### Delete media
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/media/{{mediaId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Bulk delete media
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/media/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": []
}

###

### List contents
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/contents
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List contents — pages only
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/contents?type=page
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get content
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/contents/{{contentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Create content (page)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/contents
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "about",
  "title": "About Dev Hube",
  "excerpt": "About us",
  "body": "<p>Welcome</p>",
  "type": "page",
  "status": "published"
}

###

### Update content
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/contents/{{contentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "About Dev Hube (updated)"
}

###

### Bulk content actions
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/contents/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [],
  "action": "publish",
  "status": "published"
}

###

### Delete content
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/contents/{{contentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### CMS navigation (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/navigation
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update CMS navigation
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/cms/navigation
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "id": "home",
      "label": "Home",
      "href": "/",
      "target": "_self",
      "sortOrder": 0,
      "enabled": true
    }
  ]
}

###

