### Site Kit status
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/site-kit/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### OAuth URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/site-kit/oauth/url
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### OAuth callback (paste code from Google)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/site-kit/oauth/callback
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "paste-google-auth-code-here"
}

###

### Disconnect Google
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/site-kit/disconnect
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update Site Kit settings
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/site-kit/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "siteUrl": "http://localhost:3000",
  "propertyId": "",
  "modules": {
    "analytics": true,
    "searchConsole": true,
    "pagespeed": true,
    "adsense": false
  }
}

###

### Site Kit dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/site-kit/dashboard?days=28
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

